<br>
I've grouped with clerics whose cheal would kick in at 3 bubs of health on average and clerics whose cheal would constantly kick in at less than one -- this is less difficult/risky than it used to be, now that tanks have higher AC and more HP, but regardless it takes a greater degree of ability than any other heal.<br>
<br>
